Description:
Summon down a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_FireMagic.FireStaff_Storm.Radius]}m&lt;/font&gt; radius rain of meteors for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_FireMagic.Spell_Ability_FireStaff_Storm.Duration / 1000]}s&lt;/font&gt; up to &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_FireMagic.FireStaff_Storm.CastDistance]}m&lt;/font&gt; away. Deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.FireStaff_Storm.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_fire_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage to targets upon entering the area, then deals an additional &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_FireStaff_MeteorShower_Damage.HealthModifierDamageBased * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_fire_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage every &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Status_FireStaff_MeteorShower_Damage.TickRate]}s&lt;/font&gt; while targets remain inside. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

(This effect cannot be dispelled.)&lt;/font&gt;

Costs &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[ManaCosts_Player.FireStaff_Storm.ManaCost]}&lt;/font&gt; Mana.

Cause a fiery explosion in a &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SpellDataTable_FireMagic.Spell_Ability_FireStaff_Incinerate.Radius]}m&lt;/font&gt; radius area around yourself that deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.Firestaff_Incinerate.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_fire_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage and &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;staggering&lt;/font&gt; your target. Inflicts &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;smolder&lt;/font&gt; on struck foes, dealing &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.FireStaff_Pyro_DOT.HealthModifierDamageBased * -100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_fire_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage each second for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.FireStaff_Pyro_DOT.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;. 

This ability has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)&lt;/font&gt;

Costs &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[ManaCosts_Player.FireStaff_Incinerate.ManaCost]}&lt;/font&gt; Mana.&lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;

Taunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your fire staff, hits with this ability inflict taunt for {[DamageTable.Firestaff_Incinerate.TauntDuration]}s. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)&lt;/font&gt;
